OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThieves who claimed to be police
OL,8,Fofficers as part of a burglary in
OL,9,FSurrey have been jailed for their part
OL,10,Fin what investigators described as a
OL,11,F"targeted" attack.
OL,13,FPolice received a report late on
OL,14,FJanuary 2, 2024 that three men had
OL,15,Fforced entry to an address in Ash and
OL,16,Fcommitted a burglary, after falsely
OL,17,Fsaying they were from the police.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
