OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe victim was attacked as soon as
OL,8,Fthey opened the door, with the men
OL,9,Fcutting their face with a knife before
OL,10,Ftrying to stab them in the stomach
OL,11,Fseveral times.
OL,13,FThe victim managed to block the attack
OL,14,Fusing their arm, but their hand and
OL,15,Fwrist were seriously injured.
OL,17,FTwo other people living at the house,
OL,18,Fincluding a young child, hid from the
OL,19,Fmen in a bathroom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe group then fled the home with the
OL,8,Fvictim's Rolex watch and Range Rover.
OL,10,FThe original vehicle used to travel to
OL,11,Fthe victim's address was later spotted
OL,12,Fand stopped by Sussex Police officers,
OL,13,Fwhere Karol Tomaszewski, who is 33 and
OL,14,Ffrom Littlehampton, was arrested.
OL,16,FPhone record analysis showed that
OL,17,FTomaszewski had received messages
OL,18,Fabout the intended victim and their
OL,19,Faddress, as well as messages sent
OL,20,Fafter the burglary relating to the
OL,21,FRolex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThose involved were jailed on Tuesday
OL,8,FApril 28, 2026 at Croydon Crown Court.
OL,10,FTomaszewski was sentenced to 12 years
OL,11,Fin jail, after pleading guilty to
OL,12,Fconspiracy to commit burglary and
OL,13,Fbeing found guilty of robbery and
OL,14,Fcausing grievous bodily harm (GBH)
OL,15,Fwith intent.
OL,17,FPatrick McKeown, 42, from Worthing,
OL,18,Fwas sentenced to 10 years behind bars,
OL,19,Fafter being found guilty of robbery,
OL,20,Fcausing GBH with intent and conspiracy
OL,21,Fto commit burglary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FTroy Johnson, 36, from Yapton, was
OL,8,Fjailed for three years, after pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to conspiracy to commit
OL,10,Fburglary.
OL,12,FAnd Christopher Fuller-Clarke, 49,
OL,13,Ffrom Worthing, was sentenced to 30
OL,14,Fmonths in prison, after pleading
OL,15,Fguilty to conspiracy to commit
OL,16,Fburglary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
