PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FInvestigating officer DC Caceres-Varga
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a planned and targeted
OL,9,Faggravated burglary. The offenders
OL,10,Fforced entry into the property causing
OL,11,Fsignificant fear and harm to those
OL,12,Finside, including a young child.
OL,14,F"This case demonstrates the
OL,15,Fseriousness with which we treat
OL,16,Fviolent offending in Surrey.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
