PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778170273
OL,3,CBurglars who claimed to be police
OL,4,Cofficers in 'targeted' attack are
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"We would like to thank the victims
OL,8,Ffor their courage in supporting the
OL,9,Finvestigation, and we hope this
OL,10,Foutcome offers them reassurance
OL,11,Ffollowing what was a deeply
OL,12,Fdistressing incident."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
